The Lord of the Rings (film series)

wikitext.*:
'''Wellington''' is the capital of [[New Zealand]] where many scenes of [[The Lord of the Rings (film series)|''The Lord of the Rings'' (film series)]] were filmed. It was also the location of ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King]]'' première. Later, many scenes of [[The Hobbit (film series)|''The Hobbit'' (film series)]] were filmed there too, and it was the location première of ''[[The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey]]'' as and in ''The Return of the King''.
